Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.56,0:00:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lupin, it feels so good\Nto hug and kiss you again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.60,0:00:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. But d'you know who\Ndeserves the kisses? These kids!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.39,0:00:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.74,0:00:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Hermione.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.35,0:00:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You did some amazing  back there.\NYou really are the cleverest bitch of your age.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.87,0:00:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! That makes me feel really special.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. And you! Ron!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.46,0:00:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy who's always helpin' out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.26,0:00:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for helpin' out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.76,0:00:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, no problem.\N- Cool!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.27,0:00:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And you. Little Dracula Falmoy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.15,0:00:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're little d, aren't you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.25,0:00:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure am.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get over here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.09,0:00:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To you I owe my freedom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.73,0:00:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you, count Dracula?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.94,0:00:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's this girl I like but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.12,0:00:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm not 100% positive she likes me back, so...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.57,0:00:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...shall I tell her how I feel, perhaps in a...\Na letter or... ah drawing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.39,0:00:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Or an angry e-mail?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.43,0:01:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no ,no, no. Rule no. 1, boys:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.57,0:01:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You never tell a girl that you like her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.97,0:01:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It just makes you look like an idiot.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.79,0:01:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.89,0:01:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And you. Harry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was rotting away in my cell in Azkaban, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.95,0:01:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...you know what happy thought\Nkept me going, got me through it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.16,0:01:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.77,0:01:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So thanks for saving me, Harry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.08,0:01:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to, Sirius, you...\Nyou're the only thing that I have.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.00,0:01:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are we gonna do with Peter Pettigrew?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll take his ass back to the ministry...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.89,0:01:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I'll get my charges dropped!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.65,0:01:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're gonna be a free man.\N- Sure will.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.69,0:01:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, gang.\N[Lupin is Laughing]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.44,0:01:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's hop on some brooms and head back\Nto the ministry on the double, okay?\N- Alright.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.65,0:01:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let the beautiful full moon light our way!\N- Yeah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.94,0:01:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! I mean... Shit!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.34,0:01:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaaah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.85,0:02:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, my transformation!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.00,0:02:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Lupin, my best friend.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.62,0:02:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you take your potion tonight?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.07,0:02:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.78,0:02:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaaa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.64,0:02:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lupin! You know the man you truly are!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.05,0:02:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This heart is where you live!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.43,0:02:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This heart! Right here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.84,0:02:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Transforming in the full moon?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.75,0:02:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Lupin must be a... a...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.19,0:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A gremlin!!!\N[screams]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.59,0:02:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go long, and so long!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No, he's... he's getting away!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No! We need him to prove that Sirius is innocent!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not gonna matter if I'm dead!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.21,0:02:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Remus! It's Sirius!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.34,0:02:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your best friend! Remember...\N[knock out]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.40,0:02:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Howling]\N- We're done, for it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.06,0:02:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Another howling]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What... what is that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.88,0:02:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.05,0:03:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, where is he going?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.05,0:03:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he going?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.23,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Werewolfs respond to the call of their own kind!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The forbidden forest must be crawling with them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.91,0:03:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! Like the one that chased us on Halloween!\NThe one that stole Lupins brooch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lupin, that reminds me of his best friend Sirius...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirius!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.67,0:03:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Almost.\N- Come back to me, Sirius!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.77,0:03:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean: Come back to Umbridge!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.46,0:03:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaaaah!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I [peep] caught you red handed, Harry Potter!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.37,0:03:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught you helping Sirius Black!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're not childrens no more!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.23,0:03:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're CRIMINALS!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.45,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're all gonna get the dementors kiss!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry, look! It's Dumbledore!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Umbridge, stop! Your beef isn't\Nwith these sexy boys! It's with me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.19,0:03:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbledore!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.97,0:03:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get my texts?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.56,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I got your texts! I got all ninehundred of them!\NYou've been clogging my inbox for long enough!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you didn't text me back...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.83,0:04:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbeldore, she's gone completely crazy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- She's working with deatheaters!\N- She's tried to kill Harry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, kids. But the buck stops here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.78,0:04:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Umbridge: I've tryed to be nice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.31,0:04:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tryed to be fair, but there come to time,\Nwhen you have to lay down the law!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my school and these are my chillings!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.99,0:04:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's time for you to leave and never come back!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbledore, this is just our first fight.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.27,0:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And it'll be our last.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god, Dumbledore!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.61,0:04:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why d'you be such a lousy boyfriend?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.26,0:04:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you get it, you crazy bitch?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.42,0:04:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm GAY!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, choose not to be gay then!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.08,0:04:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Umbridge, if you don't stop, I'll be forced to violence!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.74,0:04:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.50,0:04:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No Way, no how! A man\Ndoes not threaten his woman!\N[breaking Dunbledores wand]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Woah!\N- Oh...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There goes the elder wand...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.74,0:04:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the elder wand?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.87,0:04:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it doesn't matter now, Harry, ah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.82,0:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Umbridge, ah... maybe we can work something out, Huh?\N- No!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're too late!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.63,0:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, D...Dolores, I'll be your boyfriend!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.32,0:05:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,NOOOOO!\N[Echoing]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that time?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When you wouldn't talk to me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.06,0:05:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No you wouldn't talk to me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.27,0:05:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,yesterday.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We were gettin' along!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We had that little dance-y thing!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well here's a song I sing
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.53,0:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,my way,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was gonna be fine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't wanna be,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,be the man who'd be with me--
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.57,0:05:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,no way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.41,0:05:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But now you sayin' it's time--
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.38,0:05:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you gotta be like that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the way you act
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,around me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.48,0:05:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So baby come on, come on...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,well don't you tell me to go,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and say "I'm the one,"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,d-d-do you think I'm dumb?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry- did I just stutter?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.01,0:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't tell you what you know,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.18,0:05:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is the end...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.18,0:06:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You were never my friend,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you were never my--
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.45,0:06:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you were never my lover!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.73,0:06:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that night?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw you tremblin' there?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.54,0:06:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered, "I don't care,"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,about you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm rememberin' how
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.69,0:06:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you thought you were at the top,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.61,0:06:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,well I think we're better off
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,without you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.77,0:06:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got your number--
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.17,0:06:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't mean in my phone;
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,would've already just thrown it out,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.35,0:06:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,if I'd known about
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you'd bitch and moan,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,remember that way--
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,when you were way outta line?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now you're way outta time!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me what you want on your tombstone!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.99,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.04,0:07:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't you tell me to go,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.11,0:07:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,say "I'm the one,"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.78,0:07:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,d-d-do you think I'm dumb?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.78,0:07:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,sorry, did I just stutter?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.41,0:07:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't tell you what you know,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is the end...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.38,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You were never my friend,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you were never my--
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you were never my lover!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.36,0:07:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Dolores Jane Umbridge, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.39,0:07:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...hereby sentence you, Sirius Black, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.31,0:07:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...to death by the way of dementors kiss!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Umbridge, listen to reason, for god's sake!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bad you a loser.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.85,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad you waste my time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing that I'm around
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.66,0:07:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep your ass in line!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.55,0:07:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! Stop it! Let him go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.18,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him alone, you bastards!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.03,0:07:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[trying to fight the dementors off Sirius, fading out himself]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.81,0:07:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You were never my--
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you were never my lover!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.95,0:08:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Laughing]
